# Windsurf Rules

These rules govern how Windsurf assists in this repository.

## Editing

- MUST avoid speculative refactors during a feature task.
- SHOULD ask before deleting any file.

## Testing

- MUST run `pnpm test --run` before claiming a task is complete.
- SHOULD include a brief test plan in the response.

## Style

- MUST follow Prettier output exactly; no manual reformatting.
